        ":::: {#exr-distributions-8}\n",
        "if $X∼N(2,1)$, which is $\\mathbb{E}(-5X)$\n",
        "::::\n",
        "\n",
        "::: {.solution .callout-tip collapse=\"true\"}\n",
        "#### Solution:\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\\mathbb{E}(-5X)=-5\\mathbb{E}(X)=-5 \\times2=-10\n",
